Invocable Actions

Invocable actions are available through REST API. The following action has changed:

Call an Integration Procedure from a Salesforce Flow

Use the new vlocity_cmt__MediaIntegrationProcedureInvocable action.

For more information on invocable actions, see the Actions Developer Guide.
